- `/tmp/kubernetes/staging/src/k8s.io/component-base/metrics/legacyregistry/registry.go` - Global registry

**Grafana Core Metric Files:**
- `/tmp/grafana/pkg/infra/metrics/metrics.go` - Main metrics declarations and init
- `/tmp/grafana/pkg/infra/metrics/service.go` - Metrics service and registration
- `/tmp/grafana/pkg/infra/metrics/frontendmetrics.go` - Frontend metrics registration

**Prometheus Core Metric Files:**
- `/tmp/prometheus/scrape/metrics.go` - Scrape subsystem metrics (27+ metrics)
- `/tmp/prometheus/discovery/metrics.go` - Discovery subsystem metrics
- `/tmp/prometheus/cmd/prometheus/main.go` - Main binary metric registration
- `/tmp/prometheus/web/web.go` - Web UI metrics registration
